    Scope and Contents
Full-Time Faculty Personnel files from the Vice President for Academic Affairs, 1972-1992 containing faculty self evaluations, commendations, applications for tenure, evaluations by peers, students, programs, and others, and other materials related to evaluation of faculty performance. These files are used for performance evaluations relative to salary, reappointment, retention, and tenure.  
  
